{
  "texts": [
    "Adaptation to and mitigation of climate change and its impacts requires that policymakers, researchers, and engaged citizen stakeholders develop and maintain climate literacy in order to plan ahead and implement adaptations efficiently.",
    "Climate literacy refers to the capacity to synthesize information regarding the climate within varying contexts 9.",
    "Not only researchers and policymakers but also ordinary citizens can benefit from climate literacy.",
    "There are multiple reasons for this.",
    "First, with adequate climate literacy, individuals can discern the meaning and credibility (or lack of credibility) behind news articles."
  ]
}